Communication: Calgary-Cambridge, NURSE, SPIKES, Ask-Tell-Ask, teach-back. SDM with decision aids + 3-talk. Serious illness conversation (Ariadne + Vital Talk). Health literacy + cultural humility. Disclosure of errors. Goals-of-care. Multidisciplinary.

