(5) Generative AI + LLMs in healthcare: - GPT-4, Claude, Med-PaLM, others — explosive growth; - Use cases: documentation, patient communication drafts, literature summary, education, decision support; - Risks: hallucination, bias, privacy, liability, overreliance; - Validation + governance + oversight needed; - Augment not replace clinician judgment;

